      "text": "# same speed, formalized before merge\nfn charge(u) { assert authz(u);\n  stripe.charge(u.card, u.amt, idem_key) }\n  # + test: retry is a no-op", "originalText": "# same speed, formalized before merge\nfn charge(u) { assert authz(u);\n  stripe.charge(u.card, u.amt, idem_key) }\n  # + test: retry is a no-op",
